Fallout 76 Is An Absolute Nightmare is here!

I return to Fallout 76 to see if it has gotten any better. In this video I review Fallout 76’s general content which was basically me walking around completing whatever quests I felt like.

I will make a Fallout 76 part 2 in the future where I review each of the updates individually in full, including “Fallout 76 - Bitter Springs” which just came out!

I also touch a bit on Fallout 4: Anniversary edition in this vid.
